    "instructions":  "1. Combine the water and dashi granules in a medium saucepan over medium-high heat; bring to a boil.  \n\n2. Reduce heat to medium and whisk in the miso paste.  \n\n3. Stir in the diced tofu.  \n\n4. Separate the layers of the green onion, sliced diagonally into 1.25 cm pieces, and add to the soup.  \n\n5. Simmer gently for 2 to 3 minutes before serving.",
